      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project or a simple mechanical starter? This car is a diamond in the rough! While it shows significant wear and will definitely need some mechanical TLC and cosmetic attention to get it back to its best, it offers a fantastic opportunity for a bargain hunter or a DIY enthusiast. It\u2019s an honest, well-used vehicle priced to move\u2014perfect for someone looking to roll up their sleeves and save big!",
