    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, it breaks my heart a little to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy the ride. This car is in absolutely pristine condition\u2014it looks and smells just like it did on the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, keeping it garage-stored and professionally detailed. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s essentially brand new without the brand-new price tag, you\u2019ve found it. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44900.0,
