    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade vehicle in truly pristine, showroom condition. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with zero swirls or imperfections, preserved by climate-controlled garage storage and professional detailing. Inside, the cabin is flawless; the premium leather remains supple with no bolster wear, and the original floor mats are spotless. Mechanically, the car is perfect, having followed a rigorous maintenance schedule with all service records meticulously organized and available. Every electronic component, from the navigation system to the ambient lighting, functions exactly as it did the day it left the factory. With an untouched undercarriage and a spotless engine bay, this car is the definitive example for a discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
